snippet.title: kukun kun kut - Dr. Mario BS, BS Zelda AST, and Bass Tsuri Tourney previews
snippet.description:
I clipped this for the BS Zelda Homepage forums, but I figured since I got a people wanting Mario lately I'll throw in the Dr. Mario part that was just beforehand to entice them in.

This is taken from the broadcast of "Game Tora no Chou Ooana 1997/3/23.
